Dialogue: 12,0:00:35.89,0:00:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ông chủ đâu?
Dialogue: 12,0:00:36.81,0:00:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ở trong phòng.
Dialogue: 12,0:00:58.29,0:01:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Bệnh viện chỗ mẹ con bị cháy rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:01:08.76,0:01:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ!
Dialogue: 12,0:01:14.18,0:01:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Con cũng đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito ở lại đây!
Dialogue: 12,0:01:53.68,0:01:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mẹ ơi...
Dialogue: 12,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiến tranh nổ ra được ba năm, \Nmẹ tôi qua đời.
Dialogue: 12,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vào năm thứ tư, bố con tôi rời Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 12,0:02:25.33,0:02:34.05,Main,sign,0,0,0,,Thiếu niên và chim diệc
Dialogue: 12,0:02:35.97,0:02:41.10,Main,sign,0,0,0,,"Saginuma Station"
Dialogue: 12,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Đến rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cô ấy trông giống hệt mẹ tôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Để anh đợi rồi!
Dialogue: 12,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Cũng mới tới thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì là Natsuko.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì tới trễ, xin lỗi nha.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Xe bị thủng lốp giữa đường.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Lớn nhanh quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì có từng gặp con\N hồi con còn bé xíu ấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Anh qua xưởng luôn à?
Dialogue: 12,0:03:50.88,0:03:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ừm, sẽ về trước giờ cơm.
Dialogue: 12,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ái chà đúng lúc quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nào, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Nặng đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Con lên trước đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Đến biệt thự.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:30.63,0:04:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì sẽ là mẹ mới của Mahito-san đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Con biết rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Đưa tay đây dì.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Đây, ở đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Con thấy chuyển động không?
Dialogue: 12,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Em bé đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Là em gái hoặc em trai của con.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì hạnh phúc lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:04:56.98,0:04:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Dừng lại đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 12,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Nào, tới rồi đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,脇へ回して,Phiền bác chuyển hành lý qua bên kia.
Dialogue: 12,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:14.31,0:06:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Vì đây là lần đầu Mahito-san đến,\N nên sẽ đi vào từ cửa chính.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Kìa! Con nhìn xem.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tòa nhà đằng kia.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Xưởng mới của bố con đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Lúc nào qua đó xem nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ui trời, sao không có ai thế này.
Dialogue: 12,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Cầm theo giày nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Lạ thật đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Có bao giờ thấy nó \Nbay vào mái hiên đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Con diệc xanh rình mò này.
Dialogue: 12,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Chắc nó chào đón Mahito-san đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Chà chà.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Lại mở vali của Shoichi-san ra đấy à?
Dialogue: 12,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ấy đâu có, tiểu thư.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Phu xe vừa mang tới...
Dialogue: 12,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ông ấy để nó ở đây mà.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.62,Main,,1440,0,0,,Phải phải.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.54,Main,,0,960,0,,Mà đây là ai nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.54,Main,,1440,0,0,,Phải phải.
Dialogue: 12,0:08:38.91,0:08:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- Ôi có cái mùi ngòn ngọt~\N- Đúng rồi~
Dialogue: 12,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Đây là con Shoichi-san đấy!\NTên là Mahito.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:30.97,0:09:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- Gì thế?\N- Là thịt bò hộp!
Dialogue: 12,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Cho vào cơm thì ngon lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Cá hồi đóng hộp này, để phần tôi xương nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Vẫn còn thịt bò muối này.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Đây! Món cuối cùng!
Dialogue: 12,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- Là đường.\N- Có thể làm bánh nếp đậu đỏ được rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- Đậu đỏ ngọt đó~\N- Ôi ngọt, bánh nếp ngọt~
Dialogue: 12,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Ôi đường trắng tinh~\N- Để tôi nếm thử cái nào!
Dialogue: 12,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Tôi nữa.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Để con đợi rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Vẫn có những nơi còn mấy thứ này nhỉ.
Dialogue: 12,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Trông không khác gì mẹ cả.
Dialogue: 12,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Xinh trai thật ha.
Dialogue: 12,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mong là không bị làm sao.
Dialogue: 12,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Bà kia! Thuốc lá?
Dialogue: 12,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin điếu đi?
Dialogue: 12,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Đây là phòng của Mahito-san.
Dialogue: 12,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Chắc con mệt rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Để dì đi pha trà nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 12,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 12,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Con tới với mẹ đây!
Dialogue: 12,0:12:39.49,0:12:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 12,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 12,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:15:02.55,0:15:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Về thôi nào!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư đang lo lắm đấy!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Tưởng chỗ này lấp rồi mà?
Dialogue: 12,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Khéo bị bắt đi mất.
Dialogue: 12,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ơn giời cậu đây rồi!
Dialogue: 12,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Chỗ này là gì?
Dialogue: 12,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Bên trong còn có cầu thang.
Dialogue: 12,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhà kiểu gì thế?
Dialogue: 12,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,À thì...
Dialogue: 12,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Cứ nên về đã.
Dialogue: 12,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Lông đâu mất rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:05.00,0:17:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Vốn dì tính để con \Nquen với cuộc sống ở đây trước đã.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:10.76,0:17:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Tòa tháp đó là do \N{\i1}ông họ bên ngoại{\i0} của con xây.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ông thông minh lắm,
Dialogue: 12,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,nhưng vì đọc nhiều sách quá \Nmà khá kỳ quái.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vào một ngày,\N trước khi dì được sinh ra rất lâu,
Dialogue: 12,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,ông để lại cuốn sách đang đọc dở,
Dialogue: 12,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.24,Main,,0,0,0,,và bỏ đi mất tăm.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:35.24,0:17:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Dù đã tìm kiếm khắp nơi,\N cũng không tìm thấy dấu vết gì.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Rồi về sau có trận lũ lớn,
Dialogue: 12,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,hành lang nối giữa nhà chính \Nvới tháp bị sập,
Dialogue: 12,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,mới phát hiện ra có đường hầm \Nnhư mê cung bên dưới tháp.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:51.51,0:17:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Vì nguy hiểm, nên ông của dì \Nđã cho lấp lối vào.
Dialogue: 12,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san cũng đừng lại gần nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng!
Dialogue: 12,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin phép ạ!
Dialogue: 12,0:18:05.94,0:18:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Chúc dì ngủ ngon.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Con ngủ ngon.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Sáng ra lạnh đấy, nhớ đắp chăn nha.
Dialogue: 12,0:18:11.03,0:18:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:19:12.59,0:19:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito! Cứu mẹ!
Dialogue: 12,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Mừng anh về.
Dialogue: 12,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Về rồi đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hải quân giờ loạn hết cả lên rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Thế mà huênh hoang tuyên bố\N cầm cự Saipan được một năm cơ.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Bao nhiêu là người hi sinh,\N tội nghiệp quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhờ thế mà xưởng nhiều việc.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, để bố lái xe đưa con đi học.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Học sinh chuyển trường đi học bằng xe,
Dialogue: 12,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,ai cũng sốc cho xem.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Đã thưa chuyện trước với thầy cô rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Con đi cẩn thận nha.
Dialogue: 12,0:22:16.90,0:22:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, nói thật cho bố biết, là ai làm?
Dialogue: 12,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Con bị ngã thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:22:24.16,0:22:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Cứ yên tâm.
Dialogue: 12,0:22:25.85,0:22:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Bố sẽ trả thù cho con, nói thật cho bố biết đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:22:30.16,0:22:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Anh Shoichi...
Dialogue: 12,0:22:31.62,0:22:34.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Không thể bỏ qua chuyện này được!\N Đây là con trai anh!
Dialogue: 12,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Phải tới trường mới được!
Dialogue: 12,0:22:46.68,0:22:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito! Cứu với!
Dialogue: 12,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,0:22:50.93,0:22:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:13.87,0:23:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:18.38,0:23:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Đóng cái cửa này lại!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:23:59.42,0:24:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Cô chủ cứ đi nghỉ đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Ở đây để chúng tôi\N thay phiên nhau chăm sóc.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:10.57,0:27:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mày là cái thứ gì hả?
Dialogue: 12,0:27:12.41,0:27:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Đâu phải  diệc xanh bình thường đâu!
Dialogue: 12,0:27:19.99,0:27:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Xem ra đợi chờ bấy lâu nay cũng tới rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:25.17,0:27:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Nào xin mời theo tôi đi gặp thân mẫu cậu.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:28.92,0:27:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Thân mẫu?
Dialogue: 12,0:27:30.10,0:27:31.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Nói láo!
Dialogue: 12,0:27:31.47,0:27:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ tôi mất rồi!
Dialogue: 12,0:27:36.84,0:27:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Trò muôn thuở của con người đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:39.41,0:27:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Chưa có chết đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:42.00,0:27:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Nói khí không phải chứ cậu\N chưa có nhìn thấy thi hài của thân mẫu đúng không?
Dialogue: 12,0:27:50.90,0:27:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Bà ấy vẫn đang chờ cậu đến cứu đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:54.78,0:27:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin hãy qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:57.36,0:27:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin hãy qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:27:59.87,0:28:01.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin hãy qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:01.62,0:28:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:03.40,0:28:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:05.31,0:28:06.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:07.32,0:28:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:09.04,0:28:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- Qua đây.\N- Xin hãy qua đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:28:10.63,0:28:13.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:28:14.59,0:28:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:28:17.93,0:28:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,0:28:33.02,0:28:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ!
Dialogue: 12,0:28:36.32,0:28:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Đợi cậu tới đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:27.78,0:29:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu tỉnh rồi đấy à.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:30.09,0:29:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi trời tốt quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:36.91,0:29:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Mãi chẳng chịu tỉnh gì, \Nlàm cả nhà lo lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:43.22,0:29:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Còn diệc xanh...?
Dialogue: 12,0:29:44.81,0:29:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Diệc xanh?
Dialogue: 12,0:29:48.23,0:29:49.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Có diệc xanh không?
Dialogue: 12,0:29:50.06,0:29:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Chắc vẫn còn mơ à?
Dialogue: 12,0:29:51.69,0:29:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito! Tỉnh rồi đấy à.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:54.40,0:29:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Con yên tâm.
Dialogue: 12,0:29:55.76,0:29:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Bố nhất định truy cho ra thủ phạm!
Dialogue: 12,0:29:58.49,0:30:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Con chẳng may ngã thôi mà.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:00.15,0:30:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Đừng lo, chưa cần phải đi học.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:02.91,0:30:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Bố đã quyên góp 300 yên,\N lão hiệu trưởng giật cả mình luôn.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:06.99,0:30:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Đằng nào cũng chả dạy diếc gì.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:09.55,0:30:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Toàn bắt đi lao động.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:13.58,0:30:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vớ vẩn chỗ này hói đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:15.96,0:30:18.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhưng tóc dài ra thì che được thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:20.26,0:30:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko không được khỏe.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:22.56,0:30:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Chắc tại quá sức.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:24.76,0:30:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhớ đừng làm gì lo đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:29.93,0:30:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Đường sắt bị ngưng rồi, toàn sự cố này nọ.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:33.48,0:30:34.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Chóng khỏe nha con.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:35.73,0:30:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Còn lại nhờ bà nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:36.82,0:30:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:49.04,0:30:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ, đừng cố, nằm nghỉ đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:54.75,0:30:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu đi vệ sinh.
Dialogue: 12,0:30:56.96,0:30:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Có bô ở đây mà...
Dialogue: 12,0:31:21.27,0:31:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi, cái biệt thự này toàn mấy chuyện kỳ lạ.
Dialogue: 12,0:31:26.49,0:31:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Đủ kiểu trên đời.
Dialogue: 12,0:31:58.23,0:31:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Khỏe rồi đấy à?
Dialogue: 12,0:31:59.98,0:32:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:01.36,0:32:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Trông ra gì đúng không?
Dialogue: 12,0:32:03.69,0:32:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Không để ở nhà ga được\N nên đành mang tạm về đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:08.45,0:32:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Công nhận đẹp thật.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:10.53,0:32:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko lo cho con đó.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:12.82,0:32:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Đi thăm dì đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:14.87,0:32:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:16.46,0:32:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Mọi người, vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:18.70,0:32:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Nghỉ tay đi rồi về xưởng.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:27.89,0:32:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Không hợp khẩu vị Mahito-san nhỉ?
Dialogue: 12,0:32:31.95,0:32:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Không ngon chút nào.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:32.85,0:32:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Có gì nói đấy quá nhỉ.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:37.73,0:32:40.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ơ lão kia, có thuốc lá cơ à?
Dialogue: 12,0:32:43.07,0:32:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Là lá hà thủ ô. 
Dialogue: 12,0:32:44.86,0:32:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Làm bi?
Dialogue: 12,0:32:45.65,0:32:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,hHôi xin, đây cóc phải sâu bướm.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:48.49,0:32:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Thuốc lá giờ hiếm lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:32:51.83,0:32:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn vì bữa ăn.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:03.52,0:33:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư cứ dặn suốt là\N rất muốn gặp Mahito-san đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:08.72,0:33:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu đi thăm chút đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:10.68,0:33:12.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ốm nặng lắm sao?
Dialogue: 12,0:33:12.22,0:33:13.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Là ốm nghén.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:13.67,0:33:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mang thai khiến phụ nữ cực khổ nhiều lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:18.77,0:33:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu trước cũng thế đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:20.87,0:33:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Hồi mẹ cậu mang thai cậu cũng khổ lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:33:31.45,0:33:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu tới thăm dì ạ.
Dialogue: 12,0:34:03.23,0:34:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Cô chủ ơi.
Dialogue: 12,0:34:31.34,0:34:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì xin lỗi nha,\N lại để con bị thương thế này.
Dialogue: 12,0:34:37.22,0:34:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Chị ơi, em có lỗi quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:34:39.68,0:34:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư, đừng thế mà, hại người lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:34:43.15,0:34:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Mong dì sớm khỏe lại ạ!
Dialogue: 12,0:35:09.88,0:35:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Đợi cậu tới đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:36:02.21,0:36:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Thuốc lá?!
Dialogue: 12,0:36:03.58,0:36:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,たらしこん,Giời ạ! Dụ dỗ cái một luôn mà!
Dialogue: 12,0:36:47.98,0:36:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ! Cậu chủ!
Dialogue: 12,0:36:50.14,0:36:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Xíu thôi! Xíu thôi!
Dialogue: 12,0:36:52.61,0:36:53.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu đang bận rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:36:53.86,0:36:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Nói riêng cho cậu thôi đấy,\N lại đây lại đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:36:58.95,0:37:02.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ, cậu có muốn\N cung tên thật hàng thật không?
Dialogue: 12,0:37:02.83,0:37:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Có món này hợp với cậu lắm,\N hàng thật khỏi bàn.
Dialogue: 12,0:37:07.16,0:37:12.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Đầu mũi tên thì làm bằng thép này,\N rồi cây cung cũng xịn xò lắm.
Dialogue: 12,0:37:12.50,0:37:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Cứ ém đi thì chả ai biết đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:37:16.17,0:37:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Thuốc lá?
Dialogue: 12,0:37:17.80,0:37:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hikari, một bao Hikari thì sao?
Dialogue: 12,0:37:21.18,0:37:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Đưa hết cho ông kia rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:37:23.47,0:37:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hơn nữa, chỉ có 2 điếu thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:37:26.64,0:37:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Đưa cho lão già đó á?
Dialogue: 12,0:37:28.58,0:37:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Này, cậu chủ...
Dialogue: 12,0:40:03.63,0:40:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Là chữ của mẹ.
Dialogue: 12,0:40:14.85,0:40:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Là mẹ để lại cho mình.
Dialogue: 12,0:40:55.85,0:40:59.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Cô chủ ơi!
Comment: 12,0:40:59.94,0:41:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Cô chủ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:41:11.83,0:41:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Có chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 12,0:41:13.74,0:41:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Không thấy cô chủ trong phòng.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:18.96,0:41:20.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu đi với.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:36.18,0:41:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nãy cháu thấy dì đi vào rừng.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:38.10,0:41:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư á?
Dialogue: 12,0:41:39.73,0:41:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Cũng khá lâu rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:41.38,0:41:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Lúc trời còn sáng.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:43.44,0:41:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hẳn là vào rừng rồi, chắc chắn!
Dialogue: 12,0:41:45.61,0:41:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi sao lại!
Dialogue: 12,0:41:47.24,0:41:48.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Nay không thấy con diệc xanh đâu cả.
Dialogue: 12,0:41:49.95,0:41:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Lạ lắm!
Dialogue: 12,0:41:50.95,0:41:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 12,0:41:51.83,0:41:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ấy...
Dialogue: 12,0:41:56.43,0:42:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hay là thôi đi, \Ncô chủ chắc không đi lối này đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:04.39,0:42:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Chẳng nhìn thấy gì hết! \NNày cậu chủ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:42:10.55,0:42:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Dấu guốc...
Dialogue: 12,0:42:14.60,0:42:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ—
Dialogue: 12,0:42:25.36,0:42:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Bà xem.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:27.32,0:42:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Là đá lát đường.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:29.03,0:42:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,C-Có thấy gì đâu, tôi bị quáng gà mà.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:32.74,0:42:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Trước kia ở đây có đường.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:34.41,0:42:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Mà thôi về đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:36.16,0:42:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Tiểu thư không có đi vào đây đâu.
Dialogue: 12,0:42:40.66,0:42:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Nhỡ hết lựa chọn thì sao?
Dialogue: 12,0:43:08.32,0:43:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Á-Ánh sáng?! Bẫy đấy! Bẫy!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:11.99,0:43:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Thằng diệc! Tao đến rồi!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:14.69,0:43:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Trả Natsuko-san lại đây!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:17.20,0:43:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Đợi cậu tới đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:19.54,0:43:21.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Nào, mời vào!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:22.37,0:43:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Bà quay về đi, cháu sẽ vào.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:25.54,0:43:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Không được vào!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:27.09,0:43:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Tụi bà không thể nghe được\N tiếng chủ tháp.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:30.63,0:43:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Chỉ có chung huyết thống mới nghe được.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:33.68,0:43:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Vậy thì càng phải vào.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:35.75,0:43:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu phải đưa dì Natsuko về.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:37.76,0:43:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Không được.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:39.44,0:43:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Chả phải cậu cho là \Nkhông có tiểu thư Natsuko thì tốt hơn à?
Dialogue: 12,0:43:43.27,0:43:45.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Thế mà vẫn vào cứu mới lạ đấy!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:46.73,0:43:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nó bảo là mẹ cháu còn sống.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:49.07,0:43:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Dù biết là nói láo, nhưng cháu phải đi xem.
Dialogue: 12,0:43:54.24,0:43:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ấy khoan!
Dialogue: 12,0:43:55.17,0:43:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Au ui... au ui...
Dialogue: 12,0:43:59.83,0:44:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi cái lưng... au ui...
Dialogue: 12,0:44:28.11,0:44:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Đợi cậu tới đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:44:36.07,0:44:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Mời đi lối này.
Dialogue: 12,0:44:40.45,0:44:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Là bẫy đấy! Bẫy!
Dialogue: 12,0:44:42.62,0:44:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Cháu biết.
Dialogue: 12,0:44:43.87,0:44:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Biết rồi sao còn—
Dialogue: 12,0:45:23.99,0:45:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Xin mời!
Dialogue: 12,0:45:25.93,0:45:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Thân mẫu của cậu đây.
Dialogue: 12,0:45:34.67,0:45:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Có muốn lại gần xem cho rõ không?
Dialogue: 12,0:45:39.18,0:45:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Là bẫy đấy! Bẫy!
Dialogue: 12,0:45:45.77,0:45:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ơ khoan đã, cậu chủ...
Dialogue: 12,0:46:08.37,0:46:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ...
Dialogue: 12,0:46:10.50,0:46:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:46:12.50,0:46:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ ơi!
Dialogue: 12,0:46:14.67,0:46:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Mẹ—
Dialogue: 12,0:46:38.28,0:46:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ơ phí thật đấy, được làm khéo thế cơ mà.
Dialogue: 12,0:46:42.82,0:46:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Kể không chạm vào thì còn nguyên luôn.
Dialogue: 12,0:46:45.83,0:46:47.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Sao mày ác thế hả?
Dialogue: 12,0:46:47.79,0:46:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Để tôi làm lại cho xem nhé.
Dialogue: 12,0:46:51.15,0:46:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 12,0:46:52.33,0:46:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Không được báng bổ mẹ tao!
Dialogue: 12,0:46:54.04,0:46:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Bực hả? Tim ở đây này.
Dialogue: 12,0:46:57.13,0:46:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Có một mũi tên thôi, đừng có trượt.
Dialogue: 12,0:47:00.05,0:47:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Sau đó đến lượt {\i1}tao{\i0}.
Dialogue: 12,0:47:02.43,0:47:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Tao sẽ lôi trái tim sưng tấy\N vì nói dối và ngạo mạn của mày ra,
Dialogue: 12,0:47:06.37,0:47:08.64,Main,,0,0,0,,rồi cắn nát tươm!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:09.93,0:47:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Thằng hèn! Giỏi tới đây!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:13.02,0:47:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Bất tài vô dụng!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:23.61,0:47:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Đừng có đuổi theo tao!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:26.53,0:47:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Chết rồi! Là sợi lông bị rụng của mình.
Dialogue: 12,0:47:42.76,0:47:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Nguy rồi!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:45.55,0:47:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Trúng rồi! Giỏi quá!
Dialogue: 12,0:47:48.10,0:47:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mũi tên tự đuổi theo đấy chứ.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:06.62,0:48:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Thôi hỏng! Là {\i1}lông bay số 7{\i0}.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:13.16,0:48:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Nguy to rồi! Cậu làm cái gì thế hả?!
Dialogue: 12,0:48:20.88,0:48:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Cười cái gì mà cười!
Dialogue: 12,0:48:22.84,0:48:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Để cho bà biết thế nào là lễ độ.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:26.09,0:48:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ấy nhẹ tay thôi.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:42.07,0:48:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ta khép lại tại đây nhé?
Dialogue: 12,0:48:44.03,0:48:45.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Dì Natsuko ở đâu?
Dialogue: 12,0:48:45.78,0:48:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Cậu chủ à, xin thịt nướng luôn!
Dialogue: 12,0:48:49.39,0:48:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ấy...
Dialogue: 12,0:48:51.01,0:48:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mà giỏi quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:52.95,0:48:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Cho hỏi cái, sao đại ca biết được\N điểm yếu của em thế?
Dialogue: 12,0:48:57.46,0:48:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Chính mày mới nói thây.
Dialogue: 12,0:48:59.91,0:49:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Lông bay số 7.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:01.71,0:49:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ôi chết dở!
Dialogue: 12,0:49:03.73,0:49:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Không nên luyên thuyên\N một mình nhiều quá.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:06.05,0:49:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Dẫn tao đến chỗ dì Natsuko mau!
Dialogue: 12,0:49:08.93,0:49:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tốt nhất là đừng có đi.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:28.57,0:49:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Con chim đần độn kia,\N ta lệnh cho ngươi chỉ đường.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:38.50,0:49:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Thôi chịu rồi.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:41.08,0:49:43.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Có hối hận đừng trách tôi đấy.
Dialogue: 12,0:49:48.84,0:49:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Đại công cáo thành!
Dialogue: 12,0:49:53.60,0:49:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tôi không muốn...
Dialogue: 12,0:49:58.48,0:50:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Không...
Dialogue: 12,0:52:18.99,0:52:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Those who seek my knowledge shall die"...
Dialogue: 12,0:52:55.82,0:52:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 12,0:52:58.12,0:52:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 12,0:52:59.62,0:53:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 12,0:53:04.62,0:53:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 12,0:53:07.62,0:53:08.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 12,0:53:08.71,0:53:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Walk! Walk!
Dialogue: 12,0:53:15.84,0:53:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone opened the gate.
Dialogue: 12,0:53:49.29,0:53:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Get back, damn birds!
Dialogue: 12,0:54:29.50,0:54:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,On your feet.
Dialogue: 12,0:54:32.67,0:54:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 12,0:54:36.42,0:54:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Move! The buried will wake.
Dialogue: 12,0:54:46.39,0:54:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand beside me.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:17.05,0:55:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:19.59,0:55:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Walk backwards. Don't look back.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:32.56,0:55:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you open the gate?!
Dialogue: 12,0:55:35.61,0:55:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The pelicans pushed me.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:37.36,0:55:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me that arrow.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:46.28,0:55:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The gray heron? No wonder the pelicans couldn't eat you.
Dialogue: 12,0:55:57.21,0:56:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The wind is up. The tide'll be high. Follow me!
Dialogue: 12,0:56:25.07,0:56:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Push!
Dialogue: 12,0:56:45.22,0:56:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,We've caught the wind! Come!
Dialogue: 12,0:56:58.15,0:56:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That scar...
Dialogue: 12,0:57:03.11,0:57:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,My plaster came off.
Dialogue: 12,0:57:06.70,0:57:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got one too. Look.
Dialogue: 12,0:57:09.49,0:57:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A swamp thrasher got me.
Dialogue: 12,0:57:12.04,0:57:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,"Swamp thrasher"?
Dialogue: 12,0:57:13.75,0:57:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,A massive one. I ate it though.
Dialogue: 12,0:57:17.42,0:57:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,A big wave's coming. After that, plain sailing.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:11.68,0:58:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 12,0:58:14.93,0:58:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Up above.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:17.77,0:58:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a nice place?
Dialogue: 12,0:58:21.40,0:58:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Not for me.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:25.11,0:58:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a woman called Natsuko?
Dialogue: 12,0:58:29.36,0:58:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sweet on her?
Dialogue: 12,0:58:33.87,0:58:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,My father is. I'm trying to find her.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:39.62,0:58:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And what are you called?
Dialogue: 12,0:58:44.32,0:58:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:45.80,0:58:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Meaning "sincere one"...
Dialogue: 12,0:58:47.97,0:58:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's why you reek of death.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:52.80,0:58:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 12,0:58:57.56,0:58:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,None are real.
Dialogue: 12,0:59:00.14,0:59:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,In this world, the dead are the majority.
Dialogue: 12,0:59:08.82,0:59:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop rowing.
Dialogue: 12,0:59:41.89,0:59:43.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 12,0:59:43.81,0:59:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Buyers coming for our catch.
Dialogue: 12,0:59:46.86,0:59:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,They saw that flag.
Dialogue: 12,0:59:51.11,0:59:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,They're not able to kill. That's my job.
Dialogue: 12,1:00:40.41,1:00:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Get off. Help me.
Dialogue: 12,1:00:42.58,1:00:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,The warawara are coming.
Dialogue: 12,1:01:12.61,1:01:14.61,Main,,0,0,0,,No dilly-dallying!
Dialogue: 12,1:01:14.61,1:01:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That fish needs carving!
Dialogue: 12,1:01:29.75,1:01:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Lend a hand.
Dialogue: 12,1:01:54.61,1:01:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You try.
Dialogue: 12,1:02:00.99,1:02:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 12,1:02:06.46,1:02:07.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Deeper!
Dialogue: 12,1:02:14.88,1:02:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Pull hard!
Dialogue: 12,1:02:26.02,1:02:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't spill the guts!
Dialogue: 12,1:02:28.77,1:02:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Warawara eat them so they can fly.
Dialogue: 12,1:03:27.41,1:03:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, get up and eat.
Dialogue: 12,1:03:30.00,1:03:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't touch those dolls.
Dialogue: 12,1:03:59.57,1:04:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,They look like the grannies at the residence.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:05.20,1:04:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,They're protecting you.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:08.29,1:04:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Water's over there.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:34.60,1:04:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko-san.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:36.31,1:04:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know my damn name?
Dialogue: 12,1:04:39.73,1:04:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kiriko-san, right?
Dialogue: 12,1:04:41.74,1:04:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,This world isn't like mine, \Nbut some things are similar.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:47.87,1:04:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I've always been here.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:50.79,1:04:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The Kiriko-san I know is an old lady, like those dolls.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:56.04,1:04:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 12,1:04:58.38,1:04:59.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's the toilet?
Dialogue: 12,1:05:00.09,1:05:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Out there, in the yard.
Dialogue: 12,1:05:02.63,1:05:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 12,1:06:56.17,1:06:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:06:59.29,1:07:00.92,Main,,0,0,0,,They mature, then fly.
Dialogue: 12,1:07:02.33,1:07:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,They haven't flown for so long.
Dialogue: 12,1:07:16.14,1:07:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,The little ones see them off.
Dialogue: 12,1:07:18.18,1:07:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are they going?
Dialogue: 12,1:07:20.31,1:07:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,To be born.
Dialogue: 12,1:07:21.63,1:07:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 12,1:07:22.44,1:07:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Where you came from. To be born up above.
Dialogue: 12,1:07:26.11,1:07:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,As people?
Dialogue: 12,1:07:27.48,1:07:28.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 12,1:07:48.30,1:07:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we could feed them well.
Dialogue: 12,1:08:07.36,1:08:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Pelicans! Dammit, they'll eat them all!
Dialogue: 12,1:08:25.04,1:08:26.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's {*}Himi-sama{*Lady Himi}!
Dialogue: 12,1:08:42.10,1:08:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The warawara are burning!
Dialogue: 12,1:08:46.86,1:08:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't burn the warawara!
Dialogue: 12,1:08:51.11,1:08:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 12,1:08:59.45,1:09:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn birds'll stay away for now.
Dialogue: 12,1:09:02.55,1:09:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for {*}Himi-sama{*Lady Himi}, all the\N warawara would've been eaten.
Dialogue: 12,1:09:06.00,1:09:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Himi-sama{*Lady Himi}! Thank you!
Dialogue: 12,1:09:20.64,1:09:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No more'll fly tonight. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 12,1:09:51.63,1:09:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, grannies...
Dialogue: 12,1:10:38.09,1:10:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Young one, put me out of my misery.
Dialogue: 12,1:10:41.80,1:10:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,My wing is broken. I cannot fly.
Dialogue: 12,1:10:45.97,1:10:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You should've left the warawara alone!
Dialogue: 12,1:10:49.69,1:10:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,My kind were brought to this hellscape
Dialogue: 12,1:10:53.52,1:10:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,so we would eat the warawara.
Dialogue: 12,1:10:58.11,1:11:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,This sea has few fish we can eat.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:03.45,1:11:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,My kind were all starving.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:07.45,1:11:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We flew as high as we could.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:10.75,1:11:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,As high and far as our wings could carry us.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:15.00,1:11:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But... it always ended the same way.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:19.34,1:11:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We could only reach this island.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:26.06,1:11:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Now our newborns are forgetting how to fly.
Dialogue: 12,1:11:30.81,1:11:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We eat the warawara...
Dialogue: 12,1:11:33.86,1:11:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The fire maiden burns us...
Dialogue: 12,1:11:40.57,1:11:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The sea here... is cursed...
Dialogue: 12,1:11:52.68,1:11:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Rest in peace. It was such a noble pelican...
Dialogue: 12,1:12:01.76,1:12:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! You still have that?
Dialogue: 12,1:12:05.93,1:12:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 12,1:12:11.44,1:12:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko{*}-sama{*} isn't here, you know.
Dialogue: 12,1:12:13.94,1:12:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 12,1:12:15.90,1:12:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,How about I take you to her?
Dialogue: 12,1:12:19.03,1:12:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll find her myself.
Dialogue: 12,1:12:22.61,1:12:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hey, chief!
Dialogue: 12,1:12:31.12,1:12:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Arrogant little turd!
Dialogue: 12,1:12:43.01,1:12:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You're burying it?
Dialogue: 12,1:13:01.08,1:13:01.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:01.77,1:13:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm such a pushover.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:03.86,1:13:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:05.49,1:13:07.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Too far! Come back.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:09.16,1:13:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:13.00,1:13:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't stomach this.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:15.75,1:13:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if Natsuko-san gets eaten.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:19.00,1:13:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you'd eat my heart.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:27.47,1:13:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:28.55,1:13:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:32.85,1:13:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth. Where is Natsuko-san?!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:37.19,1:13:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rip this!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:38.65,1:13:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Try it! I'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:43.07,1:13:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:45.84,1:13:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 12,1:13:47.03,1:13:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay? I hardly ripped it.
Dialogue: 12,1:13:53.94,1:13:54.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's ripped now.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:10.26,1:14:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,This is crummy tea, but drink and make up.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:15.14,1:14:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't make up, because we didn't fight.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:17.39,1:14:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a liar and a cheat. I know he took Natsuko-san.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:21.94,1:14:25.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it, but you overestimate me.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:25.44,1:14:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, the wise always cheat. That's how they survive.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:28.32,1:14:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A gray heron told me all gray herons are liars.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:32.28,1:14:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that the truth, or a lie?
Dialogue: 12,1:14:35.08,1:14:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth!
Dialogue: 12,1:14:35.20,1:14:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,A lie!
Dialogue: 12,1:14:37.16,1:14:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the truth. All gray herons are liars.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:41.63,1:14:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lie too!
Dialogue: 12,1:14:42.96,1:14:44.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This lie is true.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:48.38,1:14:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a fine pair. Go search for Natsuko-san together.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:53.56,1:14:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to tend to the warawara.
Dialogue: 12,1:14:55.93,1:14:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The tower master told you to guide him, right?
Dialogue: 12,1:14:59.10,1:15:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay vigilant, and work together. Go.
Dialogue: 12,1:15:19.08,1:15:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kiriko-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:20.62,1:15:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,For good luck. Take it.
Dialogue: 12,1:15:23.75,1:15:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Will we meet again?
Dialogue: 12,1:15:25.13,1:15:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 12,1:15:26.59,1:15:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:28.09,1:15:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 12,1:15:39.64,1:15:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Natsuko-sama{*Miss Natsuko}!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:42.48,1:15:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Natsuko-sama{*Miss Natsuko}!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:48.07,1:15:51.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get some men to stay here!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:51.11,1:15:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No, the factory mustn't stop running. \NPlease return to your work.
Dialogue: 12,1:15:56.12,1:15:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! We'll always be on call!
Dialogue: 12,1:15:58.83,1:16:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 12,1:16:11.43,1:16:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,We've searched the pond, the hills, everywhere.
Dialogue: 12,1:16:16.10,1:16:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko, Mahito, and a housekeeper.
Dialogue: 12,1:16:19.02,1:16:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,A triple disappearance is unheard of.
Dialogue: 12,1:16:22.31,1:16:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Mister Shoichi...
Dialogue: 12,1:16:25.06,1:16:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Every now and then, strange things happen here...
Dialogue: 12,1:16:29.57,1:16:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been working here for a good 60 years now,
Dialogue: 12,1:16:34.74,1:16:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,and that tower out in the yard just ain't right.
Dialogue: 12,1:16:40.58,1:16:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That thing sure weren't built by people.{not a typo}
Dialogue: 12,1:16:44.12,1:16:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, scary stories now?
Dialogue: 12,1:16:47.18,1:16:51.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Just before the Meiji Revolution, it fell outta the sky!
Dialogue: 12,1:16:59.72,1:17:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Rumble rumble, BOOOOOM!
Dialogue: 12,1:17:05.06,1:17:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,With an earth-rattling crash.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:08.32,1:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You sure it wasn't just thunder?
Dialogue: 12,1:17:09.90,1:17:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There used to be a big pond, \Nbut the water all dried up.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:15.95,1:17:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That tower stands there now.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:32.92,1:17:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, Natsuko's clever granduncle had it built.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:37.93,1:17:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No siree, it came down from the sky!
Dialogue: 12,1:17:41.60,1:17:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Everybody was too scared to go near it.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:45.60,1:17:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,After 30-odd years, the forest grew back, and the thing got buried.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:51.53,1:17:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, the granduncle discovered it.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:55.73,1:17:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,He became obsessed with it.
Dialogue: 12,1:17:58.66,1:18:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Because it was so rare, \Nhe built the tower around it.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:15.88,1:18:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,So many people died or got hurt.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:19.26,1:18:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, the granduncle vanished into the tower...
Dialogue: 12,1:18:23.18,1:18:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,He sure did.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:25.35,1:18:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san's mother Hisako{*}-sama{*} also went missing once.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:32.56,1:18:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We searched the whole village.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:36.03,1:18:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Then after a year, she came back, fit as a fiddle.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:40.66,1:18:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking the same as she was before.
Dialogue: 12,1:18:43.66,1:18:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No memory of it, and grinning, but...
Dialogue: 12,1:18:49.17,1:18:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Bizarre, ain't it?
Dialogue: 12,1:18:52.71,1:18:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,We have the tower key?
Dialogue: 12,1:18:54.67,1:18:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yessir, I think...
Dialogue: 12,1:18:56.51,1:18:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go there now.
Dialogue: 12,1:19:16.07,1:19:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 12,1:19:19.15,1:19:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,These legs weren't made for walking.
Dialogue: 12,1:19:23.37,1:19:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to make it to where Natsuko{*}-sama{*} is.
Dialogue: 12,1:19:27.62,1:19:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If only I could block this hole, I could fly...
Dialogue: 12,1:19:31.94,1:19:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Shove a stick in it or something.
Dialogue: 12,1:19:34.54,1:19:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so simple. The hole maker has to fill it, or it won't work!
Dialogue: 12,1:19:40.38,1:19:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that lie true?
Dialogue: 12,1:19:42.64,1:19:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I never tell lies!
Dialogue: 12,1:19:49.89,1:19:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Be gentle...
Dialogue: 12,1:20:01.49,1:20:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Make that part smoother.
Dialogue: 12,1:20:04.16,1:20:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 12,1:20:08.00,1:20:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It's through! Gently, or you'll break your beak.
Dialogue: 12,1:20:14.46,1:20:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 12,1:20:24.18,1:20:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at me, gorgeous and powerful!
Dialogue: 12,1:20:29.60,1:20:31.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you fly?
Dialogue: 12,1:20:33.40,1:20:37.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I ain't your friend or your ally, kid.
Dialogue: 12,1:20:38.73,1:20:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So long. You'll have to find Natsuko, and get out of here,
Dialogue: 12,1:20:44.03,1:20:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,all on your lonesome...
Dialogue: 12,1:20:54.29,1:20:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It came out?
Dialogue: 12,1:20:55.83,1:20:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it just...
Dialogue: 12,1:20:58.71,1:21:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It sticks out a wee bit, so...
Dialogue: 12,1:21:01.59,1:21:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Here! This part bugs me!
Dialogue: 12,1:21:04.63,1:21:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,There! There! Oh, don't take too much off...
Dialogue: 12,1:21:07.97,1:21:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:13.97,1:21:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a home.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:15.44,1:21:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The blacksmith's. Shh! Duck down!
Dialogue: 12,1:21:23.45,1:21:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a big parakeet.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:24.99,1:21:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Weird... Why are they hanging around?
Dialogue: 12,1:21:28.91,1:21:30.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they ate the blacksmith?
Dialogue: 12,1:21:30.87,1:21:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,They eat people?!
Dialogue: 12,1:21:32.37,1:21:34.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Elephants too.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:35.17,1:21:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Like the pelicans, the master brought them, and they bred.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:41.30,1:21:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta pass through there, \Nor you can't get to Natsuko{*}-sama{*}.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:46.84,1:21:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw 'em out, then you dash in.
Dialogue: 12,1:21:50.10,1:21:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 12,1:22:53.66,1:22:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We have been waiting.
Dialogue: 12,1:22:56.83,1:23:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there a Natsuko here? I'm looking for her.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:01.84,1:23:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This way, sir.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:25.53,1:23:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:27.44,1:23:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Is this how you ate Natsuko-san?!
Dialogue: 12,1:23:31.12,1:23:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko{*}-sama{*} has baby.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:33.33,1:23:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,We not eat baby.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:35.20,1:23:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You not have baby.
Dialogue: 12,1:23:37.12,1:23:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Eatable! Eatable!
Dialogue: 12,1:23:41.42,1:23:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! It's Himi!
Dialogue: 12,1:23:59.89,1:24:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid. Those parakeets nearly stewed you.
Dialogue: 12,1:24:04.31,1:24:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Himi? Thank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 12,1:24:08.99,1:24:11.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You're that brat who was with Kiriko.
Dialogue: 12,1:24:12.78,1:24:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Mahito. I'm looking for someone called Natsuko.
Dialogue: 12,1:24:17.16,1:24:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko... My little sister?
Dialogue: 12,1:24:20.10,1:24:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Little sister?
Dialogue: 12,1:24:24.17,1:24:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 12,1:24:26.38,1:24:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Time's wasting.
Dialogue: 12,1:25:02.46,1:25:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 12,1:25:37.62,1:25:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like a tower I know.
Dialogue: 12,1:25:39.91,1:25:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's the same one.
Dialogue: 12,1:25:42.25,1:25:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It stands straddling all kinds of worlds.
Dialogue: 12,1:25:46.04,1:25:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:16.61,1:26:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:18.57,1:26:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, the jam'll drip.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:28.63,1:26:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko loves my bread too.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:34.59,1:26:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 12,1:26:36.43,1:26:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like the bread my mother used to bake!
Dialogue: 12,1:26:40.68,1:26:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko is your mother?
Dialogue: 12,1:26:42.93,1:26:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,No, she's not.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:44.85,1:26:48.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko-san is someone... my father likes.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:49.02,1:26:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,My mother died.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:51.32,1:26:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Mine did, too.
Dialogue: 12,1:26:54.23,1:26:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat up. We'll be going deep inside.
Dialogue: 12,1:27:03.87,1:27:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful. You get lost, you never get out.
Dialogue: 12,1:27:15.96,1:27:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's guarded...
Dialogue: 12,1:27:38.95,1:27:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful. In here, my power has limits.
Dialogue: 12,1:27:45.24,1:27:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 12,1:27:55.92,1:27:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Where do these doors lead?
Dialogue: 12,1:27:57.21,1:27:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Quiet. You'll mess me up.
Dialogue: 12,1:28:05.56,1:28:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 12,1:28:09.23,1:28:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get sucked in.
Dialogue: 12,1:28:15.35,1:28:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Father?!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:16.98,1:28:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your father?
Dialogue: 12,1:28:19.32,1:28:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to go home, open this.
Dialogue: 12,1:28:22.24,1:28:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What about Natsuko-san? I can't leave by myself!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:25.20,1:28:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to leave. She's having her baby.
Dialogue: 12,1:28:31.66,1:28:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Parakeets!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:38.92,1:28:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,We're trapped. In here! Turn it hard!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:42.09,1:28:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let go. Ready?
Dialogue: 12,1:28:46.26,1:28:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Grab the other knob! Shut the door!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:55.11,1:28:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 12,1:28:55.81,1:28:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 12,1:28:58.44,1:29:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Once you let go, it's lost forever.
Dialogue: 12,1:29:13.17,1:29:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,1:29:16.00,1:29:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,1:29:18.42,1:29:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 12,1:29:19.67,1:29:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Want to stay?
Dialogue: 12,1:29:20.96,1:29:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Just let go.
Dialogue: 12,1:29:22.25,1:29:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Not without Natsuko-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:29:31.80,1:29:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Taste my blade, monsters!
Dialogue: 12,1:29:47.87,1:29:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito turned into a parakeet...
Dialogue: 12,1:29:50.66,1:29:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 12,1:29:53.28,1:29:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Mister Shoichi...
Dialogue: 12,1:29:55.17,1:29:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito's a budgie now!
Dialogue: 12,1:30:34.08,1:30:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the stone.
Dialogue: 12,1:30:35.96,1:30:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not happy we're here.
Dialogue: 12,1:30:47.63,1:30:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The delivery room. Natsuko's there.
Dialogue: 12,1:30:54.64,1:30:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The stone's aware of us, \Nand upset. I wouldn't go in.
Dialogue: 12,1:30:59.94,1:31:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 12,1:31:02.48,1:31:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 12,1:31:04.68,1:31:05.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 12,1:31:53.70,1:31:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko-san, it's Mahito. Natsuko-san?
Dialogue: 12,1:32:15.26,1:32:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko-san, it's Mahito! I've come for you!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:19.64,1:32:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko-san! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:25.77,1:32:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:29.70,1:32:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back! Now!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:36.14,1:32:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:38.58,1:32:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I absolutely hate you! Get out!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:44.76,1:32:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Go back! Now!
Dialogue: 12,1:32:56.72,1:32:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother... Natsuko{*}-kaa{*}—
Dialogue: 12,1:33:03.48,1:33:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 12,1:33:08.19,1:33:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Mother! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 12,1:33:19.66,1:33:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san, run!
Dialogue: 12,1:33:24.54,1:33:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Natsuko-kaasan!{*Natsuko! Mother!}
Dialogue: 12,1:34:12.42,1:34:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Master of the great stone, hear my plea.
Dialogue: 12,1:34:17.47,1:34:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Let my sister lying there go home,
Dialogue: 12,1:34:21.20,1:34:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,with this boy who will be her son.
Dialogue: 12,1:34:27.73,1:34:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko. Natsuko. Come to me.
Dialogue: 12,1:34:32.53,1:34:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Up you get.
Dialogue: 12,1:34:39.78,1:34:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it. Good girl. Come to me.
Dialogue: 12,1:36:29.14,1:36:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You have come, my descendant.
Dialogue: 12,1:36:36.48,1:36:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Mahito.
Dialogue: 12,1:36:38.57,1:36:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the tower master? My great-granduncle?
Dialogue: 12,1:36:42.36,1:36:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait there. Quietly.
Dialogue: 12,1:37:14.31,1:37:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Now this world
Dialogue: 12,1:37:17.94,1:37:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,will last another day.
Dialogue: 12,1:37:21.65,1:37:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Another day?! It only lasts that long?
Dialogue: 12,1:37:26.08,1:37:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:24.01,1:38:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,My world,
Dialogue: 12,1:38:26.09,1:38:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,my power, everything, comes from this stone.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:31.68,1:38:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That stone created this sea world?
Dialogue: 12,1:38:35.81,1:38:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There is more to be done.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:38.52,1:38:42.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Worlds are living things. Mold and bugs infest them.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:43.40,1:38:45.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And I have grown old.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:45.78,1:38:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I seek a successor.
Dialogue: 12,1:38:51.12,1:38:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito, will you continue my work?
Dialogue: 12,1:38:55.83,1:38:57.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 12,1:38:57.42,1:39:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,My successor must come from my bloodline.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:02.55,1:39:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That is my contract with the stone.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:05.84,1:39:09.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether this world becomes beautiful,
Dialogue: 12,1:39:09.05,1:39:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,or an abomination, is entirely in your hands.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:13.60,1:39:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean your blocks?
Dialogue: 12,1:39:17.06,1:39:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You may add one of these blocks to it.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:26.53,1:39:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You can make this world a more harmonious place.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:34.87,1:39:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Those aren't wooden.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:37.04,1:39:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's stone for making tombs. It's malicious.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:44.30,1:39:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 12,1:39:45.71,1:39:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That knowledge is why I choose you.
Dialogue: 12,1:40:40.14,1:40:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 12,1:40:41.48,1:40:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Save the chit-chat!
Dialogue: 12,1:41:04.38,1:41:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi's been caught.
Dialogue: 12,1:41:05.96,1:41:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 12,1:41:07.25,1:41:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to save her!
Dialogue: 12,1:42:04.40,1:42:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Himi all right?
Dialogue: 12,1:42:05.85,1:42:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll take her to their lord.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:08.58,1:42:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Their lord?
Dialogue: 12,1:42:09.57,1:42:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Your great-granduncle.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:12.53,1:42:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll use her to make a deal with him.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:16.03,1:42:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,A deal?
Dialogue: 12,1:42:17.66,1:42:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So they get everything.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:20.12,1:42:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,The tower's full of parakeets now.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:23.83,1:42:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Your transgression gave them an excuse.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:27.04,1:42:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"Transgression"?
Dialogue: 12,1:42:28.42,1:42:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,The taboo. You entered the delivery room.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:32.13,1:42:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,A no-no.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:35.76,1:42:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But Himi didn't enter.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:37.85,1:42:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking you was taboo too.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:41.14,1:42:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a lookout.
Dialogue: 12,1:42:47.44,1:42:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Higher!
Dialogue: 12,1:42:55.78,1:43:00.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Subjects, this is far enough! Await good news!
Dialogue: 12,1:43:00.11,1:43:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us accompany you!
Dialogue: 12,1:43:02.62,1:43:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Please let us!
Dialogue: 12,1:43:05.49,1:43:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sincerity is appreciated! \NHowever, this is my duty.
Dialogue: 12,1:43:11.13,1:43:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Subjects, live well!
Dialogue: 12,1:43:16.01,1:43:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for our parakeet king!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:06.91,1:45:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Be still!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:08.58,1:45:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We carry {*}Himi-sama{*Lady Himi}, our lord's descendant!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:13.17,1:45:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yield to us!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:23.97,1:45:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Heaven!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:25.47,1:45:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Our ancestors!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:30.02,1:45:31.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Paradise!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:31.23,1:45:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, is this paradise?
Dialogue: 12,1:45:34.69,1:45:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Be silent.
Dialogue: 12,1:45:36.32,1:45:37.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 12,1:45:37.82,1:45:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So pretty...
Dialogue: 12,1:45:57.34,1:46:00.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you made it. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:01.09,1:46:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we shall walk.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:24.15,1:46:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Entering the delivery room was wrong.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:27.45,1:46:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It is no laughing matter. A grave transgression.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:32.70,1:46:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Unquestionably. The stone is shimmering dangerously.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:37.67,1:46:40.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, young souls are precious.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:41.67,1:46:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,As king, I cannot disregard a transgressor.
Dialogue: 12,1:46:46.39,1:46:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me time. I want Mahito to become my successor.
Dialogue: 12,1:47:17.21,1:47:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle...
Dialogue: 12,1:47:20.84,1:47:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We must protect our world, or it shall perish.
Dialogue: 12,1:47:24.80,1:47:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito is a good boy. It seems I must let him go.
Dialogue: 12,1:47:33.89,1:47:35.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle!
Dialogue: 12,1:47:38.35,1:47:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You must go too.
Dialogue: 12,1:48:02.71,1:48:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's it!
Dialogue: 12,1:48:04.63,1:48:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That passage.
Dialogue: 12,1:48:20.77,1:48:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been here before.
Dialogue: 12,1:48:22.69,1:48:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yow! Youch!
Dialogue: 12,1:48:28.65,1:48:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never been this far in before.
Dialogue: 12,1:48:42.63,1:48:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We should return, Majesty!
Dialogue: 12,1:48:44.84,1:48:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall go. Make sure you make it back alive,
Dialogue: 12,1:48:49.13,1:48:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,and tell them I was a true king.
Dialogue: 12,1:48:51.69,1:48:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 12,1:48:52.41,1:48:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Fare thee well!
Dialogue: 12,1:49:32.17,1:49:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey chief, ain't it time we got outta here?
Dialogue: 12,1:49:36.31,1:49:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This way. Himi's calling.
Dialogue: 12,1:49:38.97,1:49:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hear diddly-squat...
Dialogue: 12,1:49:43.81,1:49:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi!
Dialogue: 12,1:49:49.69,1:49:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,1:49:54.32,1:49:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! Are you all right? Did they hurt you?
Dialogue: 12,1:49:57.70,1:49:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 12,1:49:59.62,1:50:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd lost you. I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 12,1:50:09.00,1:50:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 12,1:50:11.22,1:50:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll go to him.
Dialogue: 12,1:50:13.47,1:50:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This feels wrong. Don't...
Dialogue: 12,1:50:15.93,1:50:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 12,1:50:21.35,1:50:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 12,1:50:27.90,1:50:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's getting dark!
Dialogue: 12,1:51:02.43,1:51:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone blocks...
Dialogue: 12,1:51:05.81,1:51:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Better not touch them. They're still powerful.
Dialogue: 12,1:51:34.88,1:51:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle, I've brought Mahito-san.
Dialogue: 12,1:51:38.30,1:51:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 12,1:51:43.14,1:51:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Look. These stones are not stained with malice.
Dialogue: 12,1:51:57.20,1:52:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I traveled the far reaches of time and space to find them.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:04.08,1:52:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,There are 13 in all. Stack them once every three days.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:10.13,1:52:15.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Build your own tower. A kingdom freed from malice.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:17.34,1:52:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Create a world of bounty, peace, and beauty.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:34.53,1:52:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this scar myself.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:37.69,1:52:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a sign of my malice.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:42.32,1:52:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't touch those stones.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:44.99,1:52:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go back with {*}Natsuko-kaasan{*Natsuko, my mother}.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:48.75,1:52:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll return to a foolish world of rampant murder and thievery?
Dialogue: 12,1:52:54.67,1:52:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon it shall be consumed by flames.
Dialogue: 12,1:52:57.97,1:53:02.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make friends. Like Himi, \NKiriko-san, and the heron man.
Dialogue: 12,1:53:03.54,1:53:04.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 12,1:53:04.60,1:53:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Make friends. Return to your world. \NBut first, stack the stones.
Dialogue: 12,1:53:10.85,1:53:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no time!
Dialogue: 12,1:53:12.94,1:53:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot keep my tower standing.
Dialogue: 12,1:53:25.99,1:53:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Traitor! You would place the fate of the empire upon mere stones?!
Dialogue: 12,1:53:39.05,1:53:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,B-Be still. Still.
Dialogue: 12,1:53:41.97,1:53:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 12,1:53:55.19,1:53:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Himi! Mahito! Return to the corridor of time!
Dialogue: 12,1:53:59.03,1:54:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,To your own time!
Dialogue: 12,1:54:01.28,1:54:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle!
Dialogue: 12,1:54:13.87,1:54:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,The planet's splitting! Grab on!
Dialogue: 12,1:54:19.67,1:54:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Too heavy...
Dialogue: 12,1:54:37.65,1:54:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Granduncle! Thank you!
Dialogue: 12,1:54:41.44,1:54:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 12,1:54:45.11,1:54:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:12.52,1:55:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Natsuko-sama{*Miss Natsuko}!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:25.78,1:55:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is it! Mahito, you go in.
Dialogue: 12,1:55:27.96,1:55:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 12,1:55:29.91,1:55:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take another door. I'm going to be your mother.
Dialogue: 12,1:55:33.91,1:55:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But you'll die in the hospital fire!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:36.71,1:55:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Fire doesn't scare me. I'll be so lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 12,1:55:40.62,1:55:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Himi, you've got to live!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:43.26,1:55:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:51.51,1:55:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Holy moly!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:55.18,1:55:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Natsuko-kaasan{*Mother}!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:56.36,1:55:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Mahito-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:57.19,1:55:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 12,1:55:58.40,1:55:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{*}Onee-sama{*Sister}.
Dialogue: 12,1:55:59.66,1:56:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope the delivery goes well.
Dialogue: 12,1:56:01.67,1:56:02.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry.
Dialogue: 12,1:56:31.64,1:56:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,How adorable!
Dialogue: 12,1:56:57.32,1:57:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! This way!
Dialogue: 12,1:57:08.76,1:57:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. The pelicans made it out too.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:12.47,1:57:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mahito.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:15.14,1:57:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember where we were?
Dialogue: 12,1:57:18.14,1:57:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:19.48,1:57:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's bad. Forget.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:21.59,1:57:22.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 12,1:57:22.56,1:57:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone{\i0} forgets. That's how it works.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:25.04,1:57:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you didn't take any keepsakes, did you?
Dialogue: 12,1:57:35.83,1:57:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a powerful charm. Way too powerful for me...
Dialogue: 12,1:57:41.46,1:57:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That's one of them stones.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:44.10,1:57:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I took it from that grassy field full of them.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:46.75,1:57:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,This is why we can't trust amateurs like you.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:49.84,1:57:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that stone ain't powerful.
Dialogue: 12,1:57:52.76,1:57:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll forget in time. As you should.
Dialogue: 12,1:58:00.43,1:58:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,So long, friend.
Dialogue: 12,1:58:14.95,1:58:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! Yeesh...
Dialogue: 12,1:58:17.03,1:58:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiriko-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:19.62,1:58:20.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The king?!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:30.96,1:58:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Natsuko! Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:33.38,1:58:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoichi-san!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:34.10,1:58:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:42.43,1:58:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two years after the war,
Dialogue: 12,1:58:46.40,1:58:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we returned to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 12,1:58:50.65,1:58:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mahito!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:54.07,1:58:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going!
Dialogue: 12,1:58:56.32,1:58:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 12,1:59:12.16,1:59:12.21,Main,chptr,0,0,0,,{Credits}
Dialogue: 12,1:59:33.07,1:59:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The clear sky on the day I was born
Dialogue: 12,1:59:40.37,1:59:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was so high, distant, and endless
Dialogue: 12,1:59:48.42,1:59:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day I heard a voice\Npatting me on the back
Dialogue: 12,1:59:55.84,2:00:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}telling me to go ahead
Dialogue: 12,2:00:02.31,2:00:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faces I met in the seasons,
Dialogue: 12,2:00:09.61,2:00:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at times hurting one another
Dialogue: 12,2:00:17.65,2:00:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shine by the light, the shadow extends
Dialogue: 12,2:00:24.79,2:00:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as the sky grows further away
Dialogue: 12,2:00:34.21,2:00:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I catch the wind and start running,\Novercoming the rubble
Dialogue: 12,2:00:40.34,2:00:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of this road,\Nsomeone is waiting for me
Dialogue: 12,2:00:46.52,2:00:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dream of light shining through,\Nat any day of the week
Dialogue: 12,2:00:55.78,2:01:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open the door this moment,\Nlike revealing hidden secrets
Dialogue: 12,2:01:01.95,2:01:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't hold myself longing for more,\Nlike the spinning globe
Dialogue: 12,2:01:20.76,2:01:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person I loved
Dialogue: 12,2:01:28.06,2:01:34.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has gone to somewhere no one knows
Dialogue: 12,2:01:36.19,2:01:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the usual kind\Nsmile as any other day,
Dialogue: 12,2:01:43.45,2:01:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}still somewhere far away
Dialogue: 12,2:01:52.58,2:01:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I take in the rain and start singing,\Nnot minding if seen
Dialogue: 12,2:01:58.88,2:02:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This road continues\Nbecause I wished it would continue
Dialogue: 12,2:02:04.97,2:02:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dream of meeting again,\Nfor ever and ever
Dialogue: 12,2:02:14.19,2:02:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I grasped the fragment firmly,\Nso the secret remains
Dialogue: 12,2:02:20.28,2:02:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep longing till the end,\Nlike the spinning globe
Dialogue: 12,2:02:32.92,2:02:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all starts from an innocent wish\Nmade long ago
Dialogue: 12,2:02:40.76,2:02:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carrying the loneliness in my heart,\NI turn the corner
Dialogue: 12,2:02:51.85,2:02:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I catch the wind and start running,\Novercoming the rubble
Dialogue: 12,2:02:58.07,2:03:04.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of this road,\Nsomeone is waiting for me
Dialogue: 12,2:03:04.20,2:03:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dream of light shining through,\Nat any day of the week
Dialogue: 12,2:03:13.41,2:03:19.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open the door this moment,\Nlike revealing hidden secrets
Dialogue: 12,2:03:19.63,2:03:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The joy of holding ones hand,\Nthe suffering of losing one
Dialogue: 12,2:03:25.80,2:03:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't hold myself from picturing,\Nlike the spinning globe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:01.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}May your luck last long in battle.\NCongratulations on your call-up.
