Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:21:01.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1158,94)}Maki Mahito
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.11,0:34:49.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hikari Cigarettes
